text: James Johnson (born 14 September 1998) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut on 26 March 2019, for Cambridge MCCU against Essex, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge MCCU cricketers Category:English cricketers of the 21st century Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
